    <item>
      <title>以色列 160 亿美元的战争法案使预算处于令人震惊的轨道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/israel-s-16-billion-war-bill-puts-budget-on-alarming-trajectory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过七个月的战争，以色列已经累积了 600 亿谢克尔（160 亿美元）的账单，如果政府不采取稳定财政的行动，其预算赤字将有可能超过今年的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/israel-s-16-billion-war-bill-puts-budget-on-alarming-trajectory</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行、渣打银行向苏纳克施压，要求放松对中国业务的打压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/hsbc-stanchart-press-sunak-to-ease-clampdown-on-china-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)政府面临汇丰控股有限公司(HSBC Holdings Plc)和渣打银行(Standard Chartered Plc)以及英国其他大公司等银行的压力，要求放松对与中国开展业务的拟议限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/hsbc-stanchart-press-sunak-to-ease-clampdown-on-china-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯的破坏、间谍活动和恐吓活动正在欧洲蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/russia-backed-agents-believed-to-be-behind-attacks-in-uk-germany-poland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在德国，俄罗斯情报部门雇佣的两名针对军事基地的犯罪嫌疑人在青少年时期就来到了该国。在爱沙尼亚，有犯罪记录的年轻人通过 Telegram 被招募来破坏部长的汽车和国家纪念碑，以换取一点现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/russia-backed-agents-believed-to-be-behind-attacks-in-uk-germany-poland</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马的穆利诺表示任何矿山谈判都将使用新机制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/panama-s-mulino-says-any-mine-talks-would-use-new-mechanism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马当选总统表示，他没有关于在这个中美洲国家重新开放一座巨型铜矿的提议，只是表示任何未来的运营模式都不会使用之前签署的“存在违宪问题”的合同类型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/panama-s-mulino-says-any-mine-talks-would-use-new-mechanism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西推出 99 亿美元计划帮助大规模洪水受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-unveils-9-9-billion-plan-to-help-victims-of-huge-floods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财政部长费尔南多·哈达德周四推出了一项价值 509 亿雷亚尔（99 亿美元）的计划，以帮助该国南部数百万人遭受洪水袭击，因为投资者对公共支出保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-unveils-9-9-billion-plan-to-help-victims-of-huge-floods</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:59:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥取消铝进口关税以应对短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/mexico-eliminates-aluminum-import-tariffs-to-combat-a-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于汽车和电子行业材料短缺，墨西哥取消了对未与其签订贸易协定的国家进口铝的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/mexico-eliminates-aluminum-import-tariffs-to-combat-a-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权、商业集团阻止加拿大资本利得税上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/private-equity-business-groups-rip-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大一些最大的商业团体敦促总理贾斯汀·特鲁多(Justin Trudeau)撤销政府提高资本利得税包含率的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/private-equity-business-groups-rip-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西历史性洪水为卢拉总统任期创造了“卡特里娜飓风时刻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-s-historic-floods-are-a-hurricane-katrina-moment-for-lula-s-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 飞越淹没该国南部地区的洪水时，他不仅调查了造成至少 107 人死亡、165,000 人流离失所的灾难，而且调查了他总统任期的决定性时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-s-historic-floods-are-a-hurricane-katrina-moment-for-lula-s-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基巩固控制权 乌克兰立法者罢免基础设施部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/ukraine-s-parliament-votes-to-dismiss-deputy-premier-kubrakov</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰立法者投票解雇了该国强大的基础设施部长，因为总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基寻求重新夺回对政府关键领域的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/ukraine-s-parliament-votes-to-dismiss-deputy-premier-kubrakov</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登警告称，若以色列袭击拉法，他将推迟部署更多武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/biden-widens-rift-with-israel-in-move-that-paused-bomb-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，如果以色列对拉法发动地面入侵，他将停止向以色列运送更多进攻性武器，并谴责可能造成的平民生命损失是“错误的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/biden-widens-rift-with-israel-in-move-that-paused-bomb-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
